Click on the right side of the drop-down menu, select the software's classification, the classification of common software name definition:
The Network = web applications;
Chat = instant messaging or social communication;
Video = Video playback;
Graphics = Graphics;
Office = Office learning;
Translation = read Translation;
Development = software Development;
The Utility = tool software or other applications.
Don't understand English can baidu query the meaning of classification of software name.
Note: the choice of software classification name determines the software package installs again after installation in the starter which classification of software directory.
